== 種類 ==
[[File:Yoshino_Sakura_Tidal_Basin_DC.jpg|thumb]]是華盛頓種類最多的櫻花]]
在現在仍存活的最初種植的12種3,020株櫻花中，大多是染井吉野櫻和關山櫻<ref name="NPS types">{{cite web |url=http://www.nps.gov/cherry/cherry-blossom-types.htm |title=Types |work=Cherry Blossom Festival |publisher=National Park Service |accessdate=2011-02-09 |archive-date=2015-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009045959/http://www.nps.gov/cherry/cherry-blossom-types.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。染井吉野櫻大多種植在潮汐湖附近，此外在北側的華盛頓紀念碑亦有種植<ref name="NPS types"/><ref name=map1>{{cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/nama/planyourvisit/upload/Tidal%20Basin.pdf|title=Tidal Basin Cherry Tree Location Map|work=Cherry Blossom Festival Maps and Brochures|publisher=National Park Service|accessdate=2011-03-31|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319191844/http://www.nps.gov/nama/planyourvisit/upload/Tidal%20Basin.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。關山櫻則主要種植在東波多馬克公園，盛開時期比染井吉野櫻要晚兩週。東波多馬克公園亦種有{{link-ja|普賢象|フゲンゾウ}}等品種<ref name="NPS types"/><ref name=map2>{{cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/nama/planyourvisit/upload/East%20PotPark.pdf|title=East Potomac Park Cherry Tree Location Map|work=Cherry Blossom Festival Maps and Brochures|publisher=National Park Service|accessdate=2011-03-31|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6gD5cLPXz?url=http://www.nps.gov/nama/planyourvisit/upload/East%20PotPark.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[枝垂櫻|枝垂櫻]]是開花較早的品種，在染井吉野櫻開花前1週開始開花。華盛頓還種植有[[大山櫻|大山櫻]]、{{link-ja|十月櫻|ジュウガツザクラ}}等品種<ref name="NPS types"/><ref name=map1/><ref name=map2/>。

